info.name: UnPlug Exts - Dark Carbon Theme
info.description:
A Dark Carbon Theme for Firefox UnPlug Extension "Result Page"...

UnPlug is a FireFox extension which lets you save video and audio which is embedded on a webpage. More info about this extension you can find here : http://unplug.mozdev.org/
info.additionalInfo:
Important (pls read) :
-------------------------
1- Firefox 2.0+ user can download the the extension here https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/2254
2- Firefox 3.0+ user can download the "fixed" version here http://www.file2go.net/view/cead20e5c2  ( originally modified by michal.dvorak & dennisn )
3- You can replace the @-moz-document url-prefix("file:///") with the one point to your actual "unplug_drencrom.html" file which are normally located at the Firefox profile.
